=======
Intent
=======
intent messaging object used to requset an aciton from other app component
communicate bet different component

you can call one acitivity to another activity is called Indent
intent is communication bet system and your application data
start, services(web browser, email, ),Broadcast(suppose your mobile is low battery, communicate pass message between os and app by intent) using by intent

two types of intent=> 
--------------------
Explicit => one activity to another acitivity you know the activity
implit => one of android app , locating some person you cant show actual map then you can take google map to google application.

